 Makoto, February 17) is a Japanese stage actress, voice actress, and choreographer from Tokyo. She is currently affiliated with tomorrow jam, and previously with Atomic Monkey (April 2014–April 1, 2021) and Stay Luck (April 1, 2021–December 1, 2024). She is sometimes miscredited as 小市 真琴.","name":"Makoto Koichi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Makoto Koichi (小市 眞琴, Koichi Makoto, 17 de febrero) es una actriz de teatro, actriz de voz y coreógrafa japonesa de Tokio. Actualmente está afiliada a tomorrow jam y anteriormente lo estuvo a Atomic Monkey (de abril de 2014 al 1 de abril de 2021) y Stay Luck (del 1 de abril de 2021 al 1 de diciembre de 2024). A veces se le acredita erróneamente como 小市 真琴.","name":"Makoto Koichi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"小市眞琴","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"小市真琴是日本的女性聲優、舞台劇女演員。出身於東京都，所屬公司為 tomorrow jam。","name":"小市真琴","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"코이치 마코토","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"Makoto Koichi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"小市真琴（日语：小市 眞琴／こいち まこと Koichi Makoto，2月17日—）是日本的女性声优、舞台演员、编舞家，东京都出身。隶属于Stay Luck。\n\n高中时就读演剧科，并开始以演戏为目标。成为声优前主要是在A-Light（A-Theater）旗下从事舞台演员的工作。2010年11月开始使用目前的艺名。演出舞台剧《幸运☆星≒音乐☆舞台》时，曾观赏动画版的《幸运☆星》作为研究，并因此对声优界产生兴趣。\n\n喜欢小孩子，曾想要成为保姆，但由于不擅长读书而放弃。","name":"小市真琴","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"มาโกโตะ โคอิจิ","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"Makoto Koiči","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Makoto Koichi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Макото Коїчі","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"小市真琴是日本的女性聲優、舞台劇女演員。出身於東京都，所屬公司為 tomorrow jam。","name":"小市真琴","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Макото Коити","primary":false}}]}},"person_2055690_translations":{"at":1773470203065,"data":{"id":2055690,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Lee Su-ji (이수지) is a South Korean comedy actress.","name":"Lee Su-ji","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"이수지","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"李秀智（이수지，Lee Su-ji），韓國喜劇演員，代表作為KBS《搞笑演唱會》，並憑此獲得2017年第44屆韓國放送大獎喜劇演員獎。","name":"李秀智","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"李秀智（朝鲜语：이수지 Lee Su-ji，1985年4月2日—），韩国喜剧演员，代表作为KBS《搞笑演唱会》，并凭此获得2017年第44届韩国放送大奖喜剧演员奖。","name":"李秀智","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"李秀智（이수지，Lee Su - ji），韓國喜劇演員，代表作為 KBS《搞笑演唱會》，並憑此獲得 2017 年第 44 屆韓國放送大獎喜劇演員獎。","name":"李秀智","primary":false}}]}},"person_432040_translations":{"at":1773491792297,"data":{"id":432040,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Thomas Luke Macfarlane is a Canadian actor and former singer. He is known for playing Scotty Wandell on the ABC television drama Brothers & Sisters (2006–2011), RAC Agent D'avin Jaqobis on the Space television science fiction series Killjoys (2015–2019), the romantic lead in a number of Hallmark Channel movies, and Aaron in Bros.","name":"Luke Macfarlane","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"Aus Wikipedia, der freien Enzyklopädie:\n\nZusammen mit seiner Zwillingsschwester Ruth besuchte Macfarlane die London Central Secondary School in seiner Heimatstadt. Er war der Frontmann der im schulischen Umfeld gegründeten Band Fellow Nameless, die er aber verließ, um in der Drama Division der Juilliard School in New York City zu studieren. Er studierte dort mit einem vierjährigen Stipendium und graduierte schließlich 2003.\n\nSeine erste Rolle in einem größeren Film bekam er 2004 in Kinsey – Die Wahrheit über Sex. Er spielte darin Bruce, den Sohn des Sexualforschers Alfred Kinsey. In der Fernsehserie Over There – Kommando Irak spielte er den Private Frank Dumphy. Von 2006 bis 2011 spielt er die Rolle des Scotty Wandell in der ABC-Serie Brothers & Sisters.\n\nSeit 2014 verkörpert er den Rick Lincoln in der Krankenhausserie The Night Shift. Seit 2015 ist er in der kanadischen SF Serie Killjoys als \"D'avin Jaqobis\" zu sehen.\n\nBeschreibung oben aus dem Wikipedia-Artikel Luke Macfarlane, lizenziert unter der Lizenz „Creative Commons Attribution/Share Alike“, vollständige Liste der Mitwirkenden auf Wikipedia.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Luke Macfarlane (19 de enero de 1980) es un actor y músico canadiense.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"Luke Macfarlane é um ator canadense. Mais conhecido por seu papel de Scotty Wandell na série norte-americana Brothers & Sisters.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja